Package ch.nolix.core.container

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IContainer<E>
    A container can store several elements of a certain type.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FPNPair
    A FPN pair (floating point number pair) contains two floating point numbers.
    List<E>
    A list is a container that can add elements at the begin or end.
    ListUsingMediator<E>  
    Matrix<E>
    A matrix is a container that stores elements in rows and columns.
    Pair<E1,E2>
    A pair contains two elements that can be of different types.
    ReadContainer<E>
    A read container provides methods to read on a given container.
    SequencePattern<E>
    A sequence pattern is a pattern for sequences.

    SubContainer<E>
    A sub container can iterate over a part of another container.
